  "difficulty": 2.5,
  "summary": "主要就是本题公式的性质不是很好找，dp 还是很好写的。",
  "link": "https://codeforces.com/problemset/problem/2183/E",
  "link_text": "Problem - 2183E - Codeforces",
  "source": "",
  "aliases": [],
